<div id='main'>
	<h1>Is my blood pressure too high?</h1>
	
	<div id='average_bp_container'>
	<% if !@average_sysbp.nil? %>
		<div id='average_bp'>
			<%= render :partial => 'average_bp', :locals => {:avsys => @average_sysbp, :avdia => @average_diabp, :bppos => @bp_position} %>
		</div>
	<% end %>
	</div>
	
	<p>Thank you.</p>
	
	<% if @warning_message %>
		<p id='warning_msg'><%= @warning_message %></p>
	<% end %>
	
	<p><%= @average_bp_message %></p>
	
	<p>...However, to get a more accurate picture of what your blood pressure is like we need to take more readings like this over the next 4 days. Some other illnesses also affect what is considered to be a healthy blood pressure - we will give you expert, personalised advice based on your individual health.</p>
	
	<% if user_signed_in? %>
		<p>Please come back to HomeBloodPressure.co.uk to take another pair of readings <span><%= @when_next_reading %></span>.</p>
	<% else %>
		<p>Sign up so you can check your blood pressure over the next 4 days and receive free personalised advice on how best to control it. We cover everything from lifestyle advice through to supplying prescriptions for medications.</p>
		<div id='sign_up'>
			<%= render :partial => 'devise/registrations/new' %>
		</div>
	<% end %>
</div>


